# UI Components

User interface elements and HUD.

## Files to Create

- **HUD.lua** - Heads-up display (health, score, lives)
- **Button.lua** - Reusable button component
- **Menu.lua** - Menu system
- **HealthBar.lua** - Health display
- **BossHealthBar.lua** - Boss health display

Ask @ui to implement all UI components and menus!
